---
title: Roasted Garlic & Veggie Flatbreads with White Sauce, Mozzarella & Chives
description: Move over, marinara—there’s a new sauce in town. In this recipe, crispy flatbreads are slathered with a rich, creamy white sauce we just can’t get enough of. We top it off with melty mozzarella and roasted garlic, plus tender zucchini and juicy marinated tomatoes. Sprinkle with chives and chili flakes if you like a little zip, then sit back and enjoy. Pizza night just got a major upgrade.
